New Records: Aiden Markram scored 91 runs, the highest by a South African in an ODI since 2016
Key Match Events: Keshav Maharaj and Tabraiz Shamsi formed a crucial last-wicket partnership of 34 runs

Pre-Game Insights: South Africa were expected to win by experts due to their batting strength

Post-Match Reflections: South Africa players celebrated their narrow win with excitement
Pakistan coach expressed frustration at the loss but praised the team's effort
Miscellaneous Highlights: The match was the first significant contest in the World Cup 2023
